Renault bought a 44% stake in Nissan in 1999 when Nissan was in better shape than $TSLA is now. They bought Nissan at roughly $2.15/share & closed 5 factories, improved design & production efficiencies. Four years later, Nissan's share price jumped to $12.80 (+495%). Turnaround.
